I hope you'll like this model, and don't hesitate to show your creations to see how great it is. Have fun!

items.name: Honolulu (Kancolle)
items.description:
An experimental character LoRA of Honolulu from Kantai Collection.

Info

Training with 98 images
Followed the manual form [ [Guide] Make your own Loras, easy and free ],
You can access to this guide in Suggested Resources section.

Recommended set up

Sampler: Euler a, DPM family series
Sampling steps: 20 or 25+
CFG Scale: 7
CLIP Skip: 2
*Do not use [restore face] on anime character!*

LoRA Weighting: [1 - 0.7], (1 - 0.55)

Baking Step:
0. Drafting (512 x 512 res to find your desired sketch)
1. Hires fix (txt2img: 768 x 768, 768 x 512, 512 x 768, or above res)
2. inpaint (img2img: refine some unwanted effect, [Euler a] with 50+ step)
3. Upscaling (img2img: res*2 with [ControlNet Tile] & Ultimate SD upscale)

Upscaler for [Step 1 - 3]: [R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B, 4x-AnimeSharp, 4x-UltraSharp]
I always skip Step 0, 2 :P

Basic prompts

HonoluluKC, (sleeveless) jacket, breast pocket, pocket, (red) ascot, (blue) skirt, (black) thighhighs, garter straps

Special outfits

HonoluluBikiniKC, (string) bikini, (white) bikini, (side-tie) bikini bottom, (red) hair flower, (flower) hair ornament

-collarbone, cleavage, navel, halterneck
-sandals, toeless footwear
-hibiscus
HonoluluKimonoKC, japanese clothes, (blue) kimono, (print) kimono, yukata, obi, ponytail

-takoyaki
-floral print, sandal
-mask, mask on head

Some additional tags that you may use for reference

-machinery, turret, rigging, rudder footwear
-headgear, (military) uniform
-twintails, twin drills
-chewing gum, bubble blowing
-blue eyes
